lyrics.stanza:
To be set free from the bond of sin,
To have the joy and peace within,
To live a life full of meaning,
Believe into the Lord.
Man's way to please God&mdash;religion;
God's way&mdash;a living Person;
Christ is God's way of salvation;
Believe and you'll be saved.

Oh what a joy! Christ now lives in us;
No longer I&mdash;how glorious!
He's daily growing within us
Till He is formed in us.
We live and walk by the Spirit,
Enjoy the fruit of the Spirit;
To Him our whole lives we commit;
All else is vanity.
